To get comb in compressed UNIX tar format via ftp:
ftp to creek3.berkeley.edu, login as anonymous. cd to pub/comb.
set type to binary. mget comb.*

i.e.:

yourmachine% ftp creek3.berkeley.edu
Connected to creek3.berkeley.edu.
220 creek3 FTP server (UNIX(r) System V Release 4.0) ready.
Name (creek3.berkeley.edu:you): anonymous
